Steemg.org Privacy Policy
 
 This is a Privacy Policy provided by steemg.org to let you know our procedures on how we handle information we get from you when you access and use our services or when you Interact with us.
By  accessing  or  using  our  Service,  you  agree  to  the  information  collection,  disclosure  and  usage as  given  in  this  Privacy  Policy.

Information Assemblage
In the course of using our site or services, We may ask, collect and store some of your information. These Information may include your IP address, referral url, destination url, search terms, geographic location and date and time of your request etc.

Cookies Information 
Steemg.org may receive information from cookies Cookies are small pieces of data your device stores about websites you visit and sends back to us when we make requests for it. Just like many sites, Cookies are required to use some or all of steemg.org services. We use this information to improve your user experience, understand user activity, and improve the quality of our Service delivery.  
However, You may at your will instruct your browser to stop accepting cookies from our site or any site. You can also set it to prompt you before accepting a cookie from the websites you visit.

Information Usage
Steemg.org takes your information security serious, We do not rent or sell any of your information to any third party person.
However we may disclose some part of your information to the Government Authorities if Requested.
All your information is used to further improve our services.

Security 
Steemg.org has put a lot of parameters in place to keep all your information safe because we take the security of all our users serious. However we do not guarantee or give a total 100 percent safety promise due to the facts that any site can be hacked.

Age 
Steemg.org is a site that works hand in hand with steemit.com and thereby operate with the official age of steemit.com . Our site just like steemit.com is open to everyone but we only collect information for people of up to 18 years and above.

Changes To Policy
Steemg.org has all the right to periodically update this Privacy Policy at any  time  we deem fit.   However,  we  will  always put up a notice on our site about the updated policy.
Your continuous usage of the site after the notice means that you accept the new policy . 

Contacting Us
